      • PointOfInterest

        public PointOfInterest(android.os.Parcel in)
        This is the Parcelable constructor for a POintOfInterest. This special constructor is required due to the implementation of the Parcelable interface and should not be removed or edited without valid reason. This Constructor is called upon trying to decode a PointOfInterest from a encoded Paraclable Object. This technique is essential for the current working of this application.

        in -
